      "span_text": "A common response to this question might describe a context with networked desktop PCs running variations of Microsoft Windows, laid out in rows in airless PC labs -\"immobile computers\"  -or a single desktop PC at the front of a lecture or seminar space, used mostly for running PowerPoint presentations."
